    "description": "探索这个有趣却又充满陷阱的世界，每翻开一张卡牌都可能带来好运或厄运。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/aade73a7c33602e7d7a87b37d6a0ccaf.poster.avif?t=1756664173\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/aade73a7c33602e7d7a87b37d6a0ccaf.webm?t=1756664173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/aade73a7c33602e7d7a87b37d6a0ccaf.mp4?t=1756664173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这片被污染的森林每次都会改变，使每场游戏都成为充满惊喜的新冒险。你能否熟练地翻开卡牌，揭开为什么到处都是垃圾的谜团？这是一款融合了策略思考、运气和探索的精彩roguelike冒险游戏，保证让你难以忘怀。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/3a7d0e196edc0acf2a5cb8a8e61dcaac.poster.avif?t=1756664173\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/3a7d0e196edc0acf2a5cb8a8e61dcaac.webm?t=1756664173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/3a7d0e196edc0acf2a5cb8a8e61dcaac.mp4?t=1756664173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>战略性战斗，每一步都至关重要。仔细选择要翻开的卡牌，明智地决定先攻击哪个垃圾怪物，用什么武器！<br></li><li>Roguelike玩法：每次失败都是向前迈进的一步。在游戏中收集卷轴，然后用它们来扩展你的卡牌池，增加你在未来探索被污染森林时的成功机会！<br></li><li>享受充满氛围的世界，感受富有活力的精美图像。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/c57a1e2a59593a2a5f14cb3a9243677b.poster.avif?t=1756664173\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/c57a1e2a59593a2a5f14cb3a9243677b.webm?t=1756664173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>灵感来自于众多出色的游戏，如<i>杀戮尖塔、影铸、Peglin、幕府将军对决、Dice &amp; Fold</i>等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/7202104b9e1ca205f1b748c6f15d77eb.poster.avif?t=1756664173\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/7202104b9e1ca205f1b748c6f15d77eb.webm?t=1756664173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069800/extras/7202104b9e1ca205f1b748c6f15d77eb.mp4?t=1756664173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
